  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>리플렛 디자인 전문</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-528941b8-a830-4863-8a00-14deaba5e066\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-350e1ca4-c266-4197-ab4f-c457d0e2c9ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-22301d5e-60a1-4593-ba8c-3abb445250c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-22301d5e-60a1-4593-ba8c-3abb445250c0\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMzFfMTEx/MDAxNzQzMzc1MTkwMTI0.rsJ0rTb2-I7JnD9itREv2YwWrm4L2BLDBBAEPLUo9Asg.P_0vI89hCcBXxdQXUl96vAzlp_KfXpO9IetlYQxaKt8g.PNG/3%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%91%EC%A7%80_3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2250\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMzFfMTEx/MDAxNzQzMzc1MTkwMTI0.rsJ0rTb2-I7JnD9itREv2YwWrm4L2BLDBBAEPLUo9Asg.P_0vI89hCcBXxdQXUl96vAzlp_KfXpO9IetlYQxaKt8g.PNG/3%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%91%EC%A7%80_3.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-afe0acc6-e425-4504-b047-89dbd506c000\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79172803-cd14-4a2f-9964-84ae37bc6e23\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e672c08e-15c4-4030-a514-eb8e32bdc112\" style=\"\">결론 먼저</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ff28272-024c-4822-9b16-bfdcf95af50d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d35ce3e-0460-440a-8b32-4b27d3df187c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-54c1cd9f-8a93-4e97-b840-0a1ad163e7e5\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>리플렛에 가장 맞는 사양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af788db2-95bf-4094-8f2d-f056ea738e76\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6c2a513-a53d-4006-b311-504684ce35d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-134e6fdf-d909-41a3-a115-e3be9ee22564\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0468b01d-c285-413d-b4d4-ccf78d9c3b2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0dfe0346-585e-4b76-914e-a6b21df5c72f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 랑데뷰나 아르떼</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3d729fc-ed29-4824-894b-da9e454ad58b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-655338a2-cb0f-4b23-a81c-d315a1ed10b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9ebf2e7-8521-47ce-82ed-53bd6f992df7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : A4를 3단으로 접는 방법</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5291639b-999e-49ce-ba30-ee9a61ee92eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-48a00762-4d78-4a93-9f54-a74e67fcdd7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15d2f94d-aed2-4b2c-ac1d-f3a4d642f366\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : UV 특수인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20820efd-a8be-4dea-984c-7ec1279034c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0353246c-3e52-41c8-97c5-79ac2ad5d3b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>접지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f5976a5d-12ca-4dd2-b6eb-73b3c0f97f7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단면 코팅, 오시(누름선)후 3단 접지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c250685-77c3-498a-9af6-3c7edc3e4664\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c6e6d9e8-dbbf-479f-a67d-f11c167bd669\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fdd34b78-940f-4447-ba5e-290bad23f696\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 박인쇄나 에폭시</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab3fcb13-29fe-4d68-9d5d-ead9eb2cbc58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a06174d1-2d4c-4100-aa32-74b01f896aac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f8a03e9-1a8c-474c-8380-c39a166ecace\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 4,000부</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09b4f600-3045-4557-8b3b-e7db1e3247e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c26ca359-7752-41ec-a670-da8da8cb8bf9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2667b455-8345-43fb-a43c-56a74b415fb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 디자인 컨펌 후 2~4일</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line7\" id=\"SE-d689f88b-7cd4-4e71-acbf-6b26535dc37d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line7 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7e14d1e7-53d9-4dc0-b599-f11294d81124\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a72a1690-c200-4e6e-8be7-4c48bf15d26c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5c4975b8-fa80-4039-81a6-7b11bdf85b49\" style=\"\">3단 리플렛 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7d90df54-f6b8-4329-a1e3-e5f25d84be8a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8c26053-6a1a-4635-baf9-45cb13b886ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76ded4b4-4bd9-47df-89be-769d8e3f2e33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">리플렛에 가장 맞는 종이에 대해 알려드릴게요. 일단 가장 저렴하면서 효율적인 종이는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8c87c444-6656-42cd-a2c4-1999843a41f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아트지/스노우지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56bd3eb2-6b0b-4df9-8e29-0a74dfb3278c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca16bdad-b393-4890-b279-8083f5b07c26\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d10883a5-fa1d-4b52-a174-a7431e8e37c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2948c557-3811-4a3f-9977-f82d1ddc8760\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1cba983c-e4d5-4f53-860c-adf9436d3b81\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아트지/스노우지의 가장 큰 차이는 유광/무광의 차이입니다. 아트지는 유광이고 스노우지는 무광입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56724548-cf61-4f6c-b990-30f6aed28527\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8096d75b-c581-41a1-bfb6-a3258f75156d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8ac72c82-0be2-488a-b8af-f7cd61ddb35d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d2523dd-e4a9-43bc-86e0-48403d15ee61\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 리플렛에 가장 효과적인 종이는 국내에서 생산되는 고급지 용지입니다. 그중에 가장 대표적인 종이가 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b63849d3-72e5-4546-a043-ec496fbbf506\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아르떼, 랑데뷰</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ade905f-7ee5-427d-9869-2b309a58a497\" style=\"color:#555555;\">지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d50ecdd2-9f2b-4e1e-96d2-c72604117e7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16f512c6-e492-49bf-8d53-109457763558\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43c5d02a-24bf-4492-b8f5-bf062d8d588f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c307bedf-38f5-418b-af4d-48cd4fd8d525\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아르떼(ARTE)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e99e0d08-c2fa-490b-b725-e3b22bee9fca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 한국제지에서 생산되는 대표적인 리플렛용 종이로 평량은 90, 105, 130, 160, 190, 210, 230, 310g이 있습니다. 색상은 크게 두 가지로 울트라화이트(고백색), 내츄럴화이트(연미색)이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dd99e067-fca5-485d-8626-eafeb3000900\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb101b42-2aa8-4b3c-ba19-aeaf94a82e57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ed89af1-a226-4e39-a3ab-bac507e42801\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e78ff7d2-afb0-4876-9a38-5325c055b59e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>랑데뷰(RENDEZVOUS)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-def103e8-0482-4795-b026-dbe0e59ceb5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">지는 삼화제지에서 생산하는 대표적인 고급지로 평량은 105, 130, 160, 190, 210, 240, 310g이 있습니다. 색상은 크게 두 가지로 내츄럴(연미색), 울트라화이트(고백색), 엑스화이트(청미색), 클래식(미색)이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9349c579-74d0-4ace-a26b-69c626d3ed2f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ca8c716-a733-4fa1-b023-95ec809913ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf7bb03d-8447-4e8a-bd93-f308d5817481\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c73f9b5e-5a58-4d19-89a6-35a88b5a4316\" style=\"color:#555555;\">각 지업 회사 사이트를 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09ed8f23-d8a6-4166-a174-4b806240bb0a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-006d9678-f161-4244-bb06-e473f688a49f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2cb48395-32c7-4376-95ec-c26315fbfb39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0291870-c89a-44c3-971e-1a4ce130e743\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그다음으로 많이 사용되는 종이는 수입지입니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f9acc82-afc6-41b3-8a7f-68cadd151258\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>반누브나 휘라레, 스타드림, 컨셉</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-097858f9-7e20-4491-9cfd-5c7e7750225b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">등이 그런 종이류입니다. 펄지나 기타 독특한 색상을 가진 종이들입니다. 다만 가격이 약간 비쌀 수 있으니 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-e876ea21-bb7d-4870-a0b0-7647119a1306\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3ac41c0c-01f3-4ccc-b77a-de56bfbf4c62\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMzFfNjIg/MDAxNzQzMzc1MjI3MTc4.uRacKWcXOGGCBqXSCgwnTt2bNS75BT8Ci7UNwDkPoeIg.gX_kdAqAx0OwX6VCDY6nXiHl_5bhhrXooCOX3dM3iukg.PNG/3%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%91%EC%A7%80_1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2250\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMzFfNjIg/MDAxNzQzMzc1MjI3MTc4.uRacKWcXOGGCBqXSCgwnTt2bNS75BT8Ci7UNwDkPoeIg.gX_kdAqAx0OwX6VCDY6nXiHl_5bhhrXooCOX3dM3iukg.PNG/3%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%91%EC%A7%80_1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b025fa6c-9ec2-4277-ae8f-91355cb