an class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a413f50-6b16-48bc-9552-280243ee259e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">위 사이즈는 210mm로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ffb05a4a-7da2-4066-90e7-76940f49b256\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db8f2afd-0bab-4c6a-b79b-d0ce7f6f599d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">생산되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-24ebc167-d17c-4dc5-b0f4-5b5c4cf8b6a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6156449-7a86-483a-bcdf-7fe25c48609d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">정확하게는 206mm로 재단됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-254c961e-8184-4cd2-8e6d-1e2c18c29022\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77c0426c-6343-4c31-a796-64926edad6fb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">이는 종이 절수와 관계된 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ea373fcb-bb16-4cec-a73d-7b366f81ce29\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-228e5387-eab7-4dd0-aeca-b4cbf917a767\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">만약 정확한 210mm로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-afe0833e-be6d-4776-887a-423946127012\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-733edbe6-4fd7-4373-9528-892408f94251\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">제작을 원하시면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --